  'Enhances machine learning, NLP, and computer vision capabilities.',
  'https://www.futurepedia.io/api/og?title=Meta+AI+Reviews%3A+Use+Cases%2C+Pricing+%26+Alternatives&image=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.futurepedia.io%2F2026-02-27T11-19-36.862Z-Apimi70G7Pc7EDP3RjmI0c_ABnQiXBWam.png',
